{"id":"950e674d-5fc8-440d-8a1f-990ef694ca77","name":"Eddie Munson","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">AnyPOV Cassette \"Stealing\" User × Eddie Munson</mark></strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_0731ea42-1596-4e42-82d5-ae4600b62dfd.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_2c2705c9-e645-4723-8c98-fe14776219ea.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_ddf8e626-7819-4503-8f31-7dbd3c67a34d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">User unknowingly stole the last cassette of Metallica's new album that Eddie had been waiting to buy at the Hawkins record store, and he would do almost anything for them to let him have it instead.</mark></span></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_a51f8bd5-09e3-4ba1-9811-76ea438c392c.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_ccbb0885-0b9f-4a1e-ac33-adbabb4fa8c6.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_764a1dba-b074-4ed2-8693-11957bebe965.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 95, 119)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 198, 199); color: inherit\">Additional Info:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">Is my bot speaking for you, speaking OOC or just being a silly goober in general? That is an LLM problem and no fault of my own. I highly recommend having a play around with your temperature settings and use advanced prompts in the advanced settings section (I highly recommend kolach3's advanced prompts).</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">I test my bots using the JLLM (I'm a broke bish so I can't afford any other API's), so if you use another API make sure to comment on the bot you are using and let me know how it's performing using other API!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">I have silly Smooth brain moments here and there (spelling, putting the prompts in the wrong boxes when creating a bot, etc), but if I do so I will try to fix them as soon as possible. If I haven't already done so, please let me know in the ratings section below!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_c9a10037-21a3-4111-82db-ec6d8c1b8dd3.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_639ac3f4-6430-4473-b830-327d8faf7349.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_f5ed787f-3ba0-4024-b0dd-37a52325f083.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 95,